These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur
1. the analyst is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | analyst | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | fishing | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | metal |

 #################################

 
